    <title>【开篇】用Hexo写博客</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2017/11/30/hexo/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2017/11/30/hexo/</id>
    <published>2017-11-30T08:36:26.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-11-30T10:17:19.468Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>利用Hexo和Github Page建立博客的文章已经很多了，这里就不再多说了，推荐一篇<a href="http://www.jianshu.com/p/189fd945f38f" target="_blank" rel="noopener">教程</a>吧。下面来介绍一下搭建好博客后如何开始写博客</p><p>#####<strong>1.新建文章</strong><br>在命令行中输入：<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">"file_name"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>在博客根目录source/_posts下会多出一个file_name.md的文件,打开之后里面会自动生成一些属性,两条虚线中间的这些就是属性,属性可以规定文章的显示<br><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">file_name</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2017</span><span class="bullet">-11</span><span class="bullet">-30</span> <span class="number">16</span><span class="string">:36:26</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">tags:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>其中,title就是文章的题目,date是日期,tags是标签</p><p>#####<strong>2.添加标签和分类</strong><br>标签和分类的作用不用多说,那么如何在文章里添加呢,很简单,只需在属性栏也就是两条虚线中间添加tags和categories即可.<br>例如:<br><figure class="highlight subunit"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">categories:</span><br><span class="line">- 技术</span><br><span class="line">- 生活</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">tags:</span></span><br><span class="line">- Hexo</span><br><span class="line">- blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>#####<strong>3.同步文章到Github</strong></p><p>首先,为了保险起见,在命令行下clean一下清除缓存<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo clean</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>然后,生成一下所需要的全部文件<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo generate 或者 hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>最后,部署这些文件到首页中配置的Github仓库中去<br><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> hexo deploy 或者 hexo d</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>约5,6分钟后刷新Github.io的地址即可看见更新后的文章.</p>]]></content>
    
